Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:42.44,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无限旋转着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:57.68,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就像爆米花弹开一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:03.02,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}喜欢这两个字在飞舞
