Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:07.05,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}AH-AH-AH-AH-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.39,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}自分に言い訳するんじゃねえ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.60,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}AH-AH-AH-AH-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.10,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}やってみなけりゃわかんねえ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.06,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}AH-AH-AH-AH-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.61,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}まっすぐ進むしかねえ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.48,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ずっと　ずっと　ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.57,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}歩き続けろ 決めた道を!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:29.20,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君の心にも 川が流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:33.91,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}汗と涙の川だ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.25,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}失敗してしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:41.63,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}流されてしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:47.34,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}やり直せばいい 弱音吐くなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.72,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}夢にしがみつくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:59.27,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}願い　叶う日が来るまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.69,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}川を渡れ! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.39,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不要为自己找借口!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.10,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}没试过又怎知道不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.61,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只能勇往直前!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.48,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不断 一直 向前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.57,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一路拼命向前 穿过决定好的路途!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:29.20,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在你眼前 奔腾的激流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:33.91,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}汗水与泪水交织的河流中!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.25,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}哪怕失败也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:41.63,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}哪怕被席卷而去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:47.34,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}都请再接再厉     切不可泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.72,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧紧抓住梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:59.27,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}直到梦想成真的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.69,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}横渡激流! You can do it!
