Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:06.49,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この涙を君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:10.95,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと君が輝くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:16.54,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ずっと見守ってた沈默の空から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:21.17,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}今 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:24.63,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あぁ 君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:29.26,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こんな僕に出来ることは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:34.39,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミの虚しさを少しでも癒すこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:39.73,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}さぁ 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:29.04,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知何时的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:33.50,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}沉睡在土壤中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:42.76,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在约定好的时间 萌生出希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.76,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}当两人相遇之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:51.81,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:55.73,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知要过多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:01.19,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花才会绽放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:06.49,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}把这颗眼泪献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:10.95,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果你能够更加闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:16.54,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我会从一直看着你的沉默的天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:21.17,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}成雨落下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:24.63,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}啊 献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:29.26,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我所能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:34.39,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就是轻轻抚慰空虚的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:39.73,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}来吧 我将成为雨
