Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\3c&HD831D9&\pos(290,595)}-被禁止的星球-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------On frame-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍摄MV
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,录综艺节目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂志采访
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选拔成员今天也很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选拔单曲马上就要发行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相反我们却一直很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经跟智惠理有差距了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选拔成员与非选拔成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理歌唱得好 长得又超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该突出的地方很突出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比起来我这样的 进不了选拔也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没进入选拔的又不只有真琴一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要沮丧到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是感叹总选举的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一场强袭演唱会已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是完全演艺禁止的星球 波罗的星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求解除限制的反政府势力和DES军之间进行着长期内战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举后的首场强袭演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由单曲选拔成员出演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们选拔成员第一场演出就是强袭演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我大显身手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打压反政府势力的士气 那边军队也会出动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 护卫队伍将会大幅增员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方和76期研究生乘上LAS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与WOTA的游击队合作 一起保护演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后77期研究生 你们也有重要的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是77期 已经潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和WOTA的情报一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现正在输送中 被要求强制劳动的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的目标维甘星是为了维护波罗的星的治安 由DGTO制造的军事要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不知为何这里有政府高管 民间企业的高层 投资家 学者出入的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的任务就是调查这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起 所有的联络都要使用暗号通信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷你们作战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧要关头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入搜查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样的变装行得通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是为了这一天才练习了演技
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论前方有怎样的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进吧 小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:05:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 危险又可怕的潜入任务…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体人员的ID确认好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们从今天开始负责补给部队的杂务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要早点回到故乡的话就给我好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东野二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几个人交给你指挥了 好好教她们怎么工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智 惠 理～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啦 一副阴沉沉的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要开始演唱会了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东野二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心潜入组的大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 现在不是担心别人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个状态很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 好好地给我干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞的话 可干不完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕的量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 开始下一个工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了倒下了可就不管你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不象样啊 就这点东西还扛不动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰要折了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用的年轻人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不干完活可没饭吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么老子要照顾这些小鬼们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大叔真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作真的很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 真琴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 感觉比平时还有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道很喜欢打扫洗手间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论打扫洗手间 还是其他活 什么都能做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我是非选拔成员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从喀秋莎那里 收到了作战开始的暗号通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在波罗的星出现00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复 在波罗的星出现00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎击部队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即停止一切演艺活动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那么大家按计划 分头开始作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 各位 华丽地开始吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哟 全机散开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新选拔组的处女舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是武器库呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 这些全是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「无尽旋转」?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是「无尽旋转」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么会在DES的基地里听到00的歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游击演唱会被监听了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了 本日的主盘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对禁止演艺活动的波罗的星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00要如何跟军事要塞波罗的星的兵力战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES军的协力企业Zodiac提供了最新式的无人战机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES的精锐将士们也是士气高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底会容忍00的演唱会进行到第几首歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5分钟 一万
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10分钟 五万
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20分钟 十万!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是现在正在进行的游击演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能延续到第几分时被阻止下来 是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 是赌场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错了 在向00的演唱会下注呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 居然对我们的演唱会做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非法的赌博交易吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这颗星球的秘密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅 假装成禁止演艺的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背地里却以此大赚一把
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再接近一些 详细调查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌场内出现入侵者?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是00的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是00?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老老实实地投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么可能听你们这些大坏蛋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00成员侵入设施内部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦发现 马上逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙她们被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信要用暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非法赌场?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00的演唱会也被用于设赌局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对被禁止的演艺活动 睁一只眼闭一只眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使DGTO获取了庞大的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一切就水落石出了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止DES的攻势都过于疲弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来都是为了使赌局变刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00抢走了DGTO的机密并逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放过任何一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能从这么多人这逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的差错导致的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但没有任何才能 也一事无成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾中的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在这里丢下如此无用的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已占领作战指挥室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始查找逃脱方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:14:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选拔成员和彼方她们拼了命地在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我明白她们的苦心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我们又怎能独自逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,织音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗小行星的中央有大型动力炉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以关闭它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既可以中断能源输出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能造成大停电
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大停电?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 就可以停止监视摄像和保卫系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 赌场也停了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点乱来 不管这正是00的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 关掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意 事情要严重起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00要关闭动力炉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后打算借机逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 这可是惊喜的展开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底00的成员能否抵达动力炉所在之处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说DES军阻止了她们的阴谋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽情下注吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要把DES军的注意力转到动力炉上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这是动摇作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们动摇也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是佯动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能倒下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让歌迷们担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 笑一个笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多DES士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可接近不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达动力炉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认DES军中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹车在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是织音她们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会 冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小真琴的两膝蹲抱转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲眼见到小真琴的消沉方式还真是独特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易把你救出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还要来危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过多亏了这 才能看到难得的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是DES中的00隐性粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东野二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 要对我的长官保密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 为什么大家都在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小真琴你却一个人在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去也帮不上任何忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有能力做偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有能力完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一事无成 一无所用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是什么都不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同是难波星出身 真替你难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不会搞笑 也没有骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂是个挫字可言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说那么明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我就是想支持这种废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举也给你投票了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4票哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么工资过得很困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键不在票数
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么是这么废柴的我?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成习惯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然蹦极跳不下去 又逊又废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你非但不隐藏废柴的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不放弃再次站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着真琴垫底的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道怎么回事 我心底的某处就温暖起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好几回都是真琴救了我哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东野先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:18:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是场苦战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把底下的基准控制中心关掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能停止动力输出了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是控制中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把中央的那根杆子折断的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大停电
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 小真琴 果然不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说也太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的话就再加把劲!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹦极时 我既不像大家那样敢跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也完全没办法积极向前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那向后就好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面向明天 全力失败
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究生的消沉担当 横沟真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战成功!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是挺能干的嘛 叽歪佛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就给你一颗星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是大逆转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00作战成功!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在停电中 必须有人来手动关门才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这分别吧 小真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也会支持你的!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流出的赌场情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经对各地都下了封口令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 情报已经被00知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:22:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能被作为丑闻暴露…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
